items.title: JetBlue flight makes emergency landing after plane loses altitude, passengers injured
items.description: A JetBlue flight made an emergency landing after experiencing a drop in altitude, leaving several passengers injured, according to the airline.

items.title: Government shutdown updates: Trump says eliminate filibuster 'NOW' to end shutdown
items.description: The Senate is now adjourned until Monday afternoon, which will mark the 34th day of the government shutdown.

items.title: What the US-China deal means for rare earths, soybean farmers and TikTok
items.description: The world's two largest economies appeared to dial back a monthslong trade war.

items.title: WATCH:  Police officer caught without pants during video court hearing
items.description: A Detroit police officer was caught during a court appearance with his pants down — literally.

items.title: WATCH:  Dog owner uses smelly socks to lure lost pet back home
items.description: A 93-year-old man has been reunited with his lost dog — thanks to a pair of smelly socks.
